node.name: Fight Club
node.description: An insomniac office worker and a devil-may-care soapmaker form an underground fight club that evolves into something much, much more.

node.name: Inception
node.description: A thief who steals corporate secrets through the use of dream-sharing technology is given the inverse task of planting an idea into the mind of a C.E.O.

node.name: Lion King
node.description: A Lion cub crown prince is tricked by a treacherous uncle into thinking he caused his father's death and flees into exile in despair, only to learn in adulthood his identity and his responsibilities.
